---
title: Sour Cream and Onion Chicken Breasts with Roasted Veggies and Creamy Pan Sauce
description: Giving tonight's dinner the favourite sour cream and onion chips treatment. All the tangy onion yumminess without any of the deep frying, this meal comes together in a flavourful flash!
